"title": "5029: knowledge, of God",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5029",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Human knowledge of God may be a purely intellectual phenomenon, as when one knows about God through observing the results of his actions, but God's people know him in a personal way because of their relationship with him.</p>\n<h2>Knowledge of God through his actions</h2>\n<h3>God acts in creation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:20\">ROM 1:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:1-Ps19:4\">PSA 19:1–19:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:17\">ACT 14:17</a></p>\n<h3>God acts in judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek38:22-Ezek38:23\">EZK 38:22–38:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:5\">EXO 7:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:4\">EXO 14:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps83:9-Ps83:18\">PSA 83:9–83:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek6:13\">EZK 6:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek39:6\">EZK 39:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek39:23\">EZK 39:23</a></p>\n<h3>God acts in saving his people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:9-Isa52:10\">ISA 52:9–52:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:46-1Sam17:47\">1SA 17:46–17:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:20\">ISA 37:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:26\">ISA 49:26</a></p>\n<h2>God's people know him through his dealings with them</h2>\n<h3>God delivers his people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod6:6-Exod6:7\">EXO 6:6–6:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod10:2\">EXO 10:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:6\">EXO 16:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:32-Deut4:35\">DEU 4:32–4:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh3:10\">JOS 3:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh4:23-Josh4:24\">JOS 4:23–4:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:13\">1KI 20:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:28\">1KI 20:28</a></p>\n<h3>God provides and cares for his people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:8\">EXO 16:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:56-1Kgs8:60\">1KI 8:56–8:60</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:17-Isa41:20\">ISA 41:17–41:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:4-Isa45:6\">ISA 45:4–45:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek37:26-Ezek37:28\">EZK 37:26–37:28</a></p>\n<h3>In giving them his law</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:19-Ezek20:20\">EZK 20:19–20:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod31:13\">EXO 31:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:11-Ezek20:12\">EZK 20:11–20:12</a></p>\n<h3>God judges and restores his people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek11:10-Ezek11:12\">EZK 11:10–11:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:34\">NUM 14:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer24:5-Jer24:7\">JER 24:5–24:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:33-Jer31:34\">JER 31:33–31:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek6:2-Ezek6:10\">EZK 6:2–6:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek7:4\">EZK 7:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek12:15-Ezek12:16\">EZK 12:15–12:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:38\">EZK 20:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:11\">EZK 36:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek37:14\">EZK 37:14</a></p>\n<h2>Knowledge of God leads to confidence in him</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:10\">PSA 9:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen22:7-Gen22:8\">GEN 22:7–22:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:25\">JOB 19:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:2\">PSA 18:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:25\">PSA 37:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:5-Ps71:6\">PSA 71:5–71:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa12:1-Isa12:2\">ISA 12:1–12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:32\">DAN 11:32</a></p>",
